name: $equivalent
desc: Coding/code "A" subsumes Coding/code "B" (e.g. B has all the properties A has, and some of it's own).

name: $subsumes
desc: Coding/code "A" is subsumed by Coding/code "B" (e.g. A has all the properties B has, and some of it's own).

name: $subsumed-by
desc: Coding/code "A" and Coding/code "B" are disjoint (e.g. each has propeties that the other doesn't have).
